data.description: Amazing location, just minutes to beach access points, schools, Highway 30A, medical facilities, parks, shopping and dining. Church Street Village has numerous community amenities including a pool, playground, clubhouse, dog park and fitness center. New HVAC 2023 May and New roof 2021. Open floor plan w/ hardwood like flooring through out, beautiful upgraded kitchen, 9' ceilings, cozy screen in covered patio. Spacious primary bedroom on 1st floor has tile shower and walk in closet.  HOA fees include all lawn and landscape maintenance, exterior pest control, facilities, management and common area upkeep. Home is vacant and available for quick move in. Welcome to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom Huff built home that seamlessly blends luxurious finishes with coastal charm. Nestled in a prime location less than 2 miles from the Cessna Landing boat ramp and 2 miles from the beach, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience and beachside tranquility. Live life to the fullest in a community that offers a pool, playground, dog park, fitness center and clubhouse. Step inside and enjoy the open-concept living area that boasts tall ceilings, large windows, and tasteful neutral tones, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, ceiling height cabinets, and elegant quartz countertops. The living room is designed for both comfort and sophistication, with a shiplap accent wall and the addition of an adjoining spacious, screened in patio. Perfect for al fresco dining and relaxation. The first floor primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting ample space, a walk-in closet and a spa-like en suite bathroom with dual vanities, upgraded countertops and trending tile selections. The two additional bedrooms upstairs are generously sized, offering versatility for guests or a home office.  Move in ready for immediate occupancy! Enjoy this close proximity to Cessna Landing boat ramp (2 miles), Ed Walline Beach Access (2 miles),  Ascension hospital and medical offices (4.5 miles) and fine dining and shopping at Grand Boulevard (5 miles). With it's perfect blend of upscale features, coastal proximity, and thoughtful design, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and luxury in a price coastal location.
